channel.title: CVE Feed for Talos -- Natus
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Talos -- Natus

item.title: CVE-2017-2860|2024-08-05T14:09:17.283Z -- talos -- natus
item.description: An exploitable denial-of-service vulnerability exists in the lookup entry functionality of KeyTrees in Natus Xltek NeuroWorks 8. A specially crafted network packet can cause an out-of-bounds read, resulting in a denial of service. An attacker can send a malicious packet to trigger this vulnerability.
